      "description": "Computational velocity profiles compared against particle image velocimetry measurements at the impeller outlet plane. Mean absolute error 4.2% across 312 measurement points; maximum local deviation 11.8% near volute tongue. Acceptance criterion of <15% mean error satisfied."
